[[Bacteria]] also exchange [[DNA]] by [[bacterial conjugation]], the benefits of which include resistance to [[antibiotic resistance|antibiotics]] and other [[toxin]]s, and the ability to utilize new [[metabolite]]s.<ref name="Baron2">{{citation
